      </References>
      <Content>In {S:04402703300034} προσδοκάω includes two significant semantic features: (1) waiting over a period of time and (2) apprehension and worry with regard to the outcome of the severe storm. It would be possible to classify προσδοκάω as simply continuing in a state over a period of time, but particularly in the context of {S:04402703300034} the element of apprehension and worry seems to be dominant.</Content>
